                <h4>Who are you and where did you first start snowboarding?</h4>
                <p>Yo, Mads here. Just a young lass who first strapped in at the prime age of 8 in Park city, UT and has become addicted to that good white stuff (snow, duh) also I could use more dogs in my life.</p>

                <h4>Why snowboarding? What drew you to it? </h4>
                <p>Actually, my dad had been boarding since the early 80s and my older brother was learning, but Park City Ski Area had just opened up to snowboarders, previously it was a skier only resort. So of course, I was not about to let them join the club without me. If my bro was gonna do it, I was gonna do it better.  I had been skiing since I was 3 years old and this was the perfect time to one up him.</p>

