                <h4>Would you rather: Grab method, Grab Japan or Grab Stalefish?</h4>
                <p>I've never done a successful Japan, methods either go great or horrible, I will never turn down a great stalefish opportunity.</p>

                <h4>What does your dream boarding trip look like? Who’s coming and where are you going? </h4>
                <p>I feel like I’ve already been on so many dream trips with so many homies. But probably would have some longtime close friends, some new soon to be best friends, maybe Japan with 3 feet of fluff each morning. Toss a nice street session in there along with a hype team and some solid après, and that my friends is the recipe for a perfect trip.</p>

                <div class="ratio ratio-16x9 mb-5"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yIgcYSQyrSk" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

                <h4>What are you listening to these days?</h4>
                <p>My music choice is all over the board most days. I honestly cannot pick any genre or artist that gets me going. Big fan of anything that slaps, whether it is some dirty south rap to some top 40 pop.</p>

                <h4>In your opinion, who is the greatest snowboarder of all-time?</h4>
                <p>Jamie Anderson is the GOAT, What can’t she do?</p>
              
